  "title": "M&E Engineer / Mechanical Engineer (Construction)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Maincon | A2 Construction Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $3800 to $5800 + AWS + VB</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Construction / M&amp;E Project Experiences</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Training Provided</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Project implementation and management of all M&amp;E works</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Ensure all M&amp;E works are perform on time, within budget and in compliance with all necessary standards, code of practice and safety regulations</strong></li>\n  <li>Responsible for the supervision and coordination of M&amp;E works at project site</li>\n  <li>Understand Main Contract /Subcontract requirement</li>\n  <li><strong>Monitor progress, quality of workmanship and compliance with requirements</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Prepare structural penetration shop-drawing for approval</strong></li>\n  <li>Prepare M&amp;E coordination drawings and liaise with Architectural Coordinators and Design Engineers to issue drawing for approval</li>\n  <li>Any other duties assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma and / or Degree in M&amp;E Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Preferably experienced in M&amp;E Projects</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now button</strong> with the following information in the resume:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
